Class Summary
FileInfo This class represents a file.
FilePart This class contains a part of a file and can be transmitted through the network.
FileSplitter This class will split a file into FileParts which can be sent to the server like packets.
FolderSaver This class is designed to save files sent from either the server or client into a specified folder.
FolderSender This class sends a folder to another computer.
